headline: Trimble Highlights AI Strategy and Innovation at Dimensions User Conference
summary: Trimble (Nasdaq: TRMB) today gave attendees of its annual user conference, Trimble Dimensions, a firsthand look at artificial intelligence (AI) innovation and the company's vision for accelerating the development and expansion of agentic AI in engineering and construction workflows.
